# Bob Watch Video Skill - API Configuration Template
# Copy this file to .env and add your actual API keys

# ============================================
# Whisper API Keys (Optional but Recommended)
# ============================================
# Only needed when videos don't have native captions
# Choose ONE of the following options:

# Option 1: Groq (Recommended - Faster & Cheaper)
# Get a free API key at: https://console.groq.com/keys
# GROQ_API_KEY=your-groq-api-key-here

# Option 2: OpenAI (Alternative)
# Get an API key at: https://platform.openai.com/api-keys
# OPENAI_API_KEY=your-openai-api-key-here

# ============================================
# Notes
# ============================================
# - Uncomment (remove #) and add your actual key
# - You only need ONE of the above keys (Groq OR OpenAI)
# - Groq is recommended: faster and cheaper
# - If you don't want transcription, use --no-whisper flag
# - Most YouTube videos have native captions (free, no API key needed)
# - API keys are only used when videos lack native captions

# ============================================
# Security
# ============================================
# - Never commit .env files with real keys to version control
# - Add .env to your .gitignore file
# - Keep this .env.example file for reference (no real keys)